%time

df2 = pd.DataFrame(columns=["Delta", "Count"])
i = 0
while i < len(df1):
    cur_sum = df1["Delta"].iloc[i]
    date = df1.index[i]
    cur_num = 1
    while (i + 1 < len(df1) ) and (df1["Vec"].iloc[i] == df1["Vec"].iloc[i + 1]):
        cur_num += 1
        cur_sum += df1["Delta"].iloc[i + 1]
        i += 1
    else:
        df2 = pd.concat([df2, pd.DataFrame({"Delta" : [cur_sum], "Count" : [cur_num]}, index=[date])])
    i += 1

In [50]:
from scipy.stats import nbinom
from scipy.stats import chisquare
In [52]:
def get_param_nbinom(obs_train):
    mean = observed.mean()
    var = observed.var()

    # param:
    p = mean / var  
    r = p * mean / (1 - p)
    
    return (r, p)

def plot_nbinom(observed, _r, _p):
    expected = nbinom.rvs(_r, _p, size = len(observed))   

    fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 1, figsize=(15, 10))
    axes.set(xlabel="Носитель")
    
    gr = pd.DataFrame({"Исходная выборка" : observed, "Сгенерированная выборка" : expected})
    sns.histplot(data=gr, bins=30, ax=axes)
    
    #sns.histplot(data=observed, bins=30, ax=axes)
    #sns.histplot(data=expected, ax=axes)
    
    #fig.tight_layout()
    #plt.show()
    
def chisquare_nbinom(obs_test, _r, _p):
    n = max(obs_test)
    f_obs = np.zeros(n)
    for i in range(n):
        f_obs[i] =  np.sum(obs_test == i)

    f_exp = np.zeros(n)
    for i in range(n):
        f_exp[i] = nbinom.pmf(i, _r, _p) * len(obs_test)

    f_exp[0] += sum(f_obs) - sum(f_exp)
    
    return chisquare(f_obs, f_exp)

from scipy.stats import gengamma
from scipy.stats import ks_2samp
In [55]:
def plot_gengamma(observed, params):
    X_gengamma = gengamma.rvs(*params, size = len(observed))
    
    fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 1, figsize=(15, 10))
    axes.set(xlabel="Носитель")
    
    gr = pd.DataFrame({"Исходная выборка" : observed, "Сгенерированная выборка" : X_gengamma})
    sns.histplot(data=gr, ax=axes)
    
    #sns.histplot(data=X, ax=axes)
    #sns.histplot(data=X_gengamma, ax=axes)
    
    #fig.tight_layout()
    #plt.show()

def ks_2samp_gengamma(X, _params):
    X_gengamma = gengamma.rvs(*params, size = len(X))
    return ks_2samp(X, X_gengamma)

observed = df2["Count"].apply(abs) - 1

X_train, X_test = train_test_split(observed, test_size=0.25, random_state=41)

r, p = get_param_nbinom(X_train)
plot_nbinom(observed, r, p)
statistic, p_value = chisquare_nbinom(X_test, r, p)

print("r = %f ; p = %f" % (r, p))
print("statistic = %f ; p_value = %f" % (statistic, p_value))
